temp = processing.correct_umis(pytest.results, 2, pytest.corrected_results.
    keys(), pytest.max_umis)
results = temp[0]
n_corrected = temp[1]
for cell_barcode in results.keys():
    for TAG in results[cell_barcode]:
        assert len(results[cell_barcode][TAG]) == len(pytest.
            corrected_results[cell_barcode][TAG])
        assert sum(results[cell_barcode][TAG].values()) == sum(pytest.
            corrected_results[cell_barcode][TAG].values())
assert n_corrected == 3
pytest.mark.dependency(depends=['test_classify_reads_multi_process'])
